title: Migrate pentobi_qml to Qt 5.7 despite QTBUG-59172 for the following reasons:
message:
Migrate pentobi_qml to Qt 5.7 despite QTBUG-59172 for the following reasons:

* backward-compatibility (Qt.labs.controls was preview module,
  QtQuick.Controls 2 is not)
* Auto-repeat with navigation buttons die not work well with Qt 5.6.
* creating a future package on F-Droid requires Qt >=5.7.

message:
